  EffectDiscription_ENG: "[Start of Your Main Phase] By placing 1 Digimon card with
    [Xros Heart] or [Blue Flare] in its traits from your hand under this Tamer, gain
    1 memory and \uFF1CDraw 1\uFF1E.[Your Turn] When you would play a Digimon card
    with a DigiXros requirement, by suspending this Tamer, you may place cards from
    under your Tamers as digivolution cards for a DigiXros."
